+# Deployment Conformance
+
+Release 238 upgrades the service-worker cache identity to 238, uses a focused
+core and route-consumer precache, includes the explicit effective registry and
+its three consumers, and forbids the retired `site-directory.js` path and global
+Fetch API replacement.
